txt.en: A large force of Variags have sacked and then made camp at the hamlet of Bâr Nadhron in the Beacon Hills. Reducing their numbers will throw them into disarray and safe-guard nearby Ost Rimmon from assault.
You have defeated many Variags in Bâr Nadhron.
You have defeated many Variags in Bâr Nadhron in the Beacon Hills.
You should defeat Variags in Bâr Nadhron in the Beacon Hills of Far Anórien.
Defeat a number of the Variags who have made camp at Bâr Nadhron in the Beacon Hills.
